data.title: Town Without Pity 1961 UK Quad Film Poster
data.meta_description: A menacing Kirk Douglas glowers in the striking and powerful UK quad for 60s drama Town Without Pity. Year 1961 Poster Type UK Quad (30 x 40 inches) Style  -  Art By  -  Rolled/Folded/Other Folded Condition EX/NM     Condition Details Small tear and crease on top border. Couple of pinholes and very light wear on folds
data.text: Each of our carefully researched, styled, tested and distributed collections reflects a particular aesthetic and ethos. We hope some of these speak to your own style, and help you refine and redefine your own look and style philosophy in the process.
